Class ApplicantFilterManager

java.lang.Object
managers.ApplicantFilterManager
public class ApplicantFilterManager extends Object
The ApplicantFilterManager class provides filtering capabilities for a list of Application objects based on various user-defined criteria.

These criteria include project name, neighborhood, flat type, project, opening/closing dates, marital status, and applicant age range.
